ðŸŽ¯ Sample Advanced Code Examples
âœ… Find nth Highest Salary

java
Copy
Edit
Optional<Integer> nthSalary = salaries.stream()
    .distinct()
    .sorted(Comparator.reverseOrder())
    .skip(n - 1)
    .findFirst();
âœ… Group Students by Pass/Fail

java
Copy
Edit
Map<Boolean, List<Student>> partitioned = students.stream()
    .collect(Collectors.partitioningBy(s -> s.getMarks() >= 40));
âœ… Top 3 Frequent Words in Paragraph

java
Copy
Edit
Map<String, Long> freq = Arrays.stream(paragraph.split("\\s+"))
    .collect(Collectors.groupingBy(Function.identity(), Collectors.counting()));

freq.entrySet().stream()
    .sorted(Map.Entry.<String, Long>comparingByValue().reversed())
    .limit(3)
    .forEach(System.out::println);
âœ… Find All Anagrams Together

java
Copy
Edit
Map<String, List<String>> groupedAnagrams = words.stream()
    .collect(Collectors.groupingBy(word -> {
        char[] chars = word.toCharArray();
        Arrays.sort(chars);
        return new String(chars);
    }));

ðŸ“š Examples of Some Key Codes
âœ… Find Even Numbers from List

java
Copy
Edit
List<Integer> evens = numbers.stream()
                             .filter(n -> n % 2 == 0)
                             .collect(Collectors.toList());
âœ… Group by First Character

java
Copy
Edit
Map<Character, List<String>> grouped = words.stream()
        .collect(Collectors.groupingBy(word -> word.charAt(0)));
âœ… Find Maximum Salary Employee

java
Copy
Edit
Optional<Employee> highestPaid = employees.stream()
        .max(Comparator.comparing(Employee::getSalary));
âœ… Find Duplicates

java
Copy
Edit
Set<Integer> duplicates = list.stream()
    .filter(i -> Collections.frequency(list, i) > 1)
    .collect(Collectors.toSet());

